</p>
You can even unfollow all the podcasts, you followed so far at once, by clicking &nbsp;
<.link href={follow_frontend_path(@conn, :unfollow_all_podcasts)} method="delete" data-confirm="Are you sure? All podcasts will be unfollowed!" class="btn btn-error whitespace-nowrap leading-10">
  {icon("exclamation-heroicons-outline")} Unfollow all podcasts
</.link>

<ul class="list-disc m-4">
