<h2 class="text-2xl mb-4 mt-8">Recommendations</h2>

<p class="mb-2">
  You can delete a recommendation by clicking the Delete button next to it. <br />
  You can double check the context by clicking the podcast or episode link, that will open
  podcast or episode in a new tab, respectively.
</p>
You can even delete all the recommendations, you created so far, at once, by clicking &nbsp;
<.link href={recommendation_frontend_path(@conn, :delete_all)} method="delete" data-confirm="Are you sure? All recommendations will be deleted!" class="btn btn-error whitespace-nowrap leading-10">
  {icon("exclamation-heroicons-outline")} Delete all recommendations
</.link>

<table class="table table-zebra table-xs my-4 w-auto">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Object</th>
      <th>Date</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Comment</th>
      <th>Actions</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <%= for recommendation <- @user.recommendations do %>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <%= cond do %>
            <% recommendation.podcast -> %>
              Podcast: <.link href={podcast_frontend_path(@conn, :show, recommendation.podcast)} target="_blank" class="text-link hover:text-link-dark">{recommendation.podcast.title}</.link>
            <% recommendation.episode -> %>
              Episode: <.link href={episode_frontend_path(@conn, :show, recommendation.episode)} target="_blank" class="text-link hover:text-link-dark">{recommendation.episode.title}</.link>
            <% recommendation.chapter -> %>
              <.link href={episode_frontend_path(@conn, :show, recommendation.chapter.episode_id)} target="_blank" class="text-link hover:text-link-dark">{recommendation.chapter.title}</.link>
          <% end %>
        </td>
        <td>
          <nobr>
            <%= Calendar.strftime(recommendation.inserted_at, "%c") %>
          </nobr>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><%= recommendation.comment %></td>
        <td class="text-center">
          <.link href={recommendation_frontend_path(@conn, :delete, recommendation)} method="delete" data-confirm="Are you sure?" class="border border-gray bg-danger hover:bg-danger-light text-white py-1 px-2 text-sm rounded-md">Delete</.link>
        </td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="bg-danger-light/50 p-4 max-w-xl rounded-xl my-4">
  <h2 class="text-lg text-danger-dark">
    Danger Zone
  </h2>

  <p class="mb-4">
    You can of course delete your account. This will delete all your data as well.
    <br />We would be really sad to see you leave. But you can always sign up for a new account.
  </p>

  <.link href={user_frontend_path(@conn, :delete_my_account)} method="delete" data-confirm="Are you sure? Your account would be deleted!" class="btn btn-error">
    {icon("exclamation-heroicons-outline")} Delete my account
  </.link>
</div>
